data.description: Beautiful, spacious home located off Ingram and Callaghan Rd in the Aspen Garden Subdivision. This home has an open concept floorplan to the main living area, separate dining area and breakfast bar. The kitchen includes a walk in pantry/ utility room. All rooms and 2nd living area are on the second level. The 2nd living area has a built in desk with access to the full guest bathroom and all bedrooms. The main bedroom is approx. 20x 14 ft. and features a full bath and walk in closet. Kitchen cabinets, half bath and guest bath vanities and carpet were replaced in June 2020. Minutes from Ingram Park Mall, less than 20 minutes to Sea World and Downtown San Antonio. Schedule your viewing today and make this your forever home!
